Class CasParserTestDouble

    CasParser

    public final class CasParserTestDouble
extends Object
implements CasParser
    CasParserTestDouble is a CasParser implementation that will allow CasFileVisitors to get visit messages from arbitrary cas data without needing a real cas file.
